a certain amount of funds

00:35:56.542 --> 00:35:58.000
and write them off
at the beginning

00:35:58.000 --> 00:35:59.660
of the year-- write
them off-- there is

00:35:59.660 --> 00:36:01.040
no return on
investment required.

00:36:01.040 --> 00:36:03.269
They're written off, but
you can play with them,

00:36:03.269 --> 00:36:05.060
and you give them to
different departments,

00:36:05.060 --> 00:36:08.280
it will allow more innovation.

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:10.040
Retail.

00:36:10.040 --> 00:36:12.430
Like I said earlier,
we've gone into retail,

00:36:12.430 --> 00:36:14.180
not because we're
interested in retailers,

00:36:14.180 --> 00:36:16.740
because our retailers don't
