I've been told I've
got two minutes.

00:36:59.969 --> 00:37:03.030
I've now got about 45 seconds.

00:37:03.030 --> 00:37:10.269
In summary, businesses,
we are growing.

00:37:10.269 --> 00:37:11.060
We're still little.

00:37:11.060 --> 00:37:12.150
We're 32 million.

00:37:12.150 --> 00:37:13.640
We've grown while
