00:37:23.780 --> 00:37:26.010
But my job is to disrupt.

00:37:26.010 --> 00:37:34.560
My job is to agitate and
to not be too serious

00:37:34.560 --> 00:37:41.950
and to not start worrying too
much about what might or might

00:37:41.950 --> 00:37:45.270
not happen and to
continue to be different.

00:37:45.270 --> 00:37:49.020
And I've been there 14 years.

00:37:49.020 --> 00:37:50.260
In theory, I should be stale.

00:37:50.260 --> 00:37:51.750
I'm frustrated we
haven't even got

00:37:51.750 --> 00:37:53.830
started with the
amount of stuff we

00:37:53.830 --> 00:37:57.480
should be doing
with this business.

00:37:57.480 --> 00:38:02.700
And I think that-- and remain--
my ambition for the business,

00:38:02.700 --> 00:38:04.760
and I hope similarly
for our staff is not

00:38:04.760 --> 00:38:06.150
how much dosh I can have.

00:38:06.150 --> 00:38:07.900
When you meet an
80-year-old, they

00:38:07.900 --> 00:38:09.980
don't give a stuff how
much dosh they've got,

00:38:09.980 --> 00:38:12.390
and all that crap
they've accumulated

00:38:12.390 --> 00:38:14.051
over their life,
most of it's rubbish.

00:38:14.051 --> 00:38:15.550
What they care about
is what they've

00:38:15.550 --> 00:38:18.970
delivered to society, what their
legacy is, what effect they've

00:38:18.970 --> 00:38:21.150
had on this little
planet of ours.

00:38:21.150 --> 00:38:24.290
And in this business,
in every business,

00:38:24.290 --> 00:38:27.040
that is the opportunity.

00:38:27.040 --> 00:38:29.480
And if you can deliver
on that, then you've

00:38:29.480 --> 00:38:31.250
delivered something worthwhile.

